Business Scenario
Product managers want to understand how credit limits are distributed across different card families (Silver, Gold, Platinum, etc.). This helps ensure that product positioning and risk appetite are aligned.

Your Task
Using the Card_base table, for each Card_Family:

Find the minimum credit limit
Find the maximum credit limit
Return one row per card family with its lowest and highest credit limit.

select
  card_family,
  min(credit_limit) as min_credit_limit,
  max(credit_limit) as max_credit_limit
from
  card_base
group by
  card_family
order by
  card_family
